posts.post_title: WTB: Cobb, Mathewson, Wilhelm T205s Beater/Low Grade
posts.post_content: I'm almost done with a complete low grade T205 set (front variations only), with much help from many of you on this board. I'm looking for the last three cards - Cobb, Mathewson, and Wilhelm - in low grades or raw. For example my Walter Johnson has a corner missing that runs the second baseline. Please let me know if you have any available or any leads, thanks!
